comment: Great Study, hope to do more in the future.
This was a very fun study, I wonder how well I did.

You need to have a few more obvious attention checks and not threaten to reject people if they don't mark every other one as being the same. Some still had small differences, even though you wanted them to be marked the same. The longer I did this, the more I felt like I should not have bothered & that you're just looking for an excuse to reject and not pay for my time. Hoping I'm wrong.
Interesting study.  Thank you for allowing me to participate.

I'm just so worried about whether I did a good job. I was completely focused and I tried very hard. However, I missed some of the practice ones, so I'm a bit scared of how I did despite my best effort. Thank you!
Doing it well was hard, longer than 20 minutes. No prob though.
